One of the best places in Long Island to spend your day with kids has many rides suitable for every age, but you now have to pay for entry regardless of whether or not you intend to go on any rides. You can check ticket prices from below link;

https://adventureland.us/tickets-pricing/

The food court offers many options, and you can buy drinks and ice cream from stalls throughout the park. However, mornings are busy, so you'll have to wait in line for rides. If you go after 4 pm on a weekday, there will be fewer crowds, and you likely won't have to wait in line.

